ritical\n        publicoverridevoid CriticalVirtual() { }\n    }\n\n}\n</pre>\n\n\n\n\n\n</p><h2>MSDN Documentation</h2>\n<p><a href="http://msdn.microsoft.com/en-us/library/dd997447.aspx" target="_blank">http://msdn.microsoft.com/en-us/library/dd997447.aspx</a></p>	2	\N	READY	cs	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	LINEAR	\N	10min	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	f	HTML	1511453806784	1511453806786	1
